fb02fccbf&scene=21#wechat_redirect)\\n\\n**[03](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485785&idx=1&sn=0562beb23b37ac99e26535216ff10679&chksm=e983b089def4399fed6c83ef622903587d04c1ede3b000b8515c2a072042fe9b113ddf04aca5&scene=21#wechat_redirect)**[ 过去十年的硅谷VC都发生过什么大事？](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485785&idx=1&sn=0562beb23b37ac99e26535216ff10679&chksm=e983b089def4399fed6c83ef622903587d04c1ede3b000b8515c2a072042fe9b113ddf04aca5&scene=21#wechat_redirect)\\n\\n**[02](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485377&idx=1&sn=39d081752b1e18231672199b7e65b7ef&chksm=e983be11def43707dffc99de88825923732325051148e1c9812ac94931902afdf770e433d0c3&scene=21#wechat_redirect)**[ 这群人在网页上重新建立了硅谷 ](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485377&idx=1&sn=39d081752b1e18231672199b7e65b7ef&chksm=e983be11def43707dffc99de88825923732325051148e1c9812ac94931902afdf770e433d0c3&scene=21#wechat_redirect)\\n\\n**[01](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485042&idx=1&sn=7f0c4b18cc2228417dc1e3f48d8f0383&chksm=e983bfa2def436b4842d53ccf59e328711d4bd31f60e7ec44073f24ee7c58dcd5a28f37cdedf&scene=21#wechat_redirect)**[ A16Z怎么看下个10年的美国？](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485042&idx=1&sn=7f0c4b18cc2228417dc1e3f48d8f0383&chksm=e983bfa2def436b4842d53ccf59e328711d4bd31f60e7ec44073f24ee7c58dcd5a28f37cdedf&scene=21#wechat_redirect)\\n\\n![]()\\n\\n现在微信公众号打乱了时间线，如果你不特地点进来，很可能看不到本号了。希望喜欢【溯元育新】的读者朋友们将本号【设为星标★】，方便找到我们；也欢迎点击右下角的【在看】。\\n\\n![]()\\n\\n![]()\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640590953,\"title\":\"创新正在抑制我们的进步  | 溯元周报\"},\"digest\":\"vWsKqFYLPQU9Qml8vfy9h3YORg0WgLIHKsMpbslcPig\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8a8b0bf3911F48D74c323246935880DAA9064bE2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kq3RzOFC7HhsaMUPdEEJlKUV9HKz_Rp5sq7C_WWLgrM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NuDxaETHc4Z2ZkZ5gyDVynXEXIjKXlj8JFmTWJe-PjU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"sTW5O1KYJKgl8ZOVjFDXjoY1O10LitF3ULqGazX-n6OUtrfg0d4kMejJFQw1dRKkgBN6QXpXw9CJRQSap2qcuw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb2902e2f97cda407eb25c9afd71e6c79d3a3ea95d7e6c5281688fde185ba52f22f0188b0a347d99ebb1d84829334c71fc2bc2c5ccb9e9272f28acff50302c71b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kq3RzOFC7HhsaMUPdEEJlKUV9HKz_Rp5sq7C_WWLgrM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NuDxaETHc4Z2ZkZ5gyDVynXEXIjKXlj8JFmTWJe-PjU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"vWsKqFYLPQU9Qml8vfy9h3YORg0WgLIHKsMpbslcPig\"}"